      </div>

        <div class="summary-synopsis"><p>Like <a href="#mapfoldl/3"><code class="inline">mapfoldl/3</code></a> but skips default-valued entries.</p></div>

    </div>


    <div class="summary-row">
      <div class="summary-signature">
        <a href="#sparse_mapfoldl/5" data-no-tooltip="" translate="no">sparse_mapfoldl(Low, High, Function, InitialAcc, Array)</a>

      </div>

        <div class="summary-synopsis"><p>Like <a href="#mapfoldl/5"><code class="inline">mapfoldl/5</code></a> but skips default-valued entries.</p></div>

    </div>


    <div class="summary-row">
      <div class="summary-signature">
        <a href="#sparse_mapfoldr/3" data-no-tooltip="" translate="no">sparse_mapfoldr(Function, InitialAcc, Array)</a>

      </div>

        <div class="summary-synopsis"><p>Like <a href="#mapfoldr/3"><code class="inline">mapfoldr/3</code></a> but skips default-valued entries.</p></div>

    </div>


    <div class="summary-row">
      <div class="summary-signature">
        <a href="#sparse_mapfoldr/5" data-no-tooltip="" translate="no">sparse_mapfoldr(Low, High, Function, InitialAcc, Array)</a>

      </div>

        <div class="summary-synopsis"><p>Like <a href="#mapfoldr/5"><code class="inline">mapfoldr/5</code></a> but skips default-valued entries.</p></div>

    </div>


    <div class="summary-row">
      <div class="summary-signature">
        <a href="#sparse_size/1" data-no-tooltip="" translate="no">sparse_size(Array)</a>

      </div>

        <div class="summary-synopsis"><p>Gets the number of entries in the array up until the last non-default-valued
entry.</p></div>

    </div>


    <div class="summary-row">
      <div class="summary-signature">
        <a href="#sparse_to_list/1" data-no-tooltip="" translate="no">sparse_to_list(Array)</a>

      </div>

        <div class="summary-synopsis"><p>Converts the array to a list, skipping default-valued entries.</p></div>

    </div>


    <div class="summary-row">
