        <div class="specs">

            <pre translate="no"><span class="attribute">-opaque</span> array(Type)</pre>

        </div>


<p>A functional, extendible array.</p><p>The representation is not documented and is subject to change without
notice. Notice that arrays cannot be directly compared for equality.</p>
