  <section class="docstring">



<p>Append a single value to the right side of the array.</p><p>The operation is always allowed even if the array is fixed.</p><h2 id="append/2-examples" class="section-heading"><a href="#append/2-examples" class="hover-link"><i class="ri-link-m" aria-hidden="true"></i></a><span class="text">Examples</span></h2><pre><code class="makeup erlang" translate="no"><span class="gp unselectable">1&gt; </span><span class="n">A</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nc">array</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="nf">from_list</span><span class="p" data-group-id="5435234980-1">(</span><span class="nc">lists</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="nf">seq</span><span class="p" data-group-id="5435234980-2">(</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="mi">9</span><span class="p" data-group-id="5435234980-2">)</span><span class="p" data-group-id="5435234980-1">)</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="w">
</span><span class="gp unselectable">2&gt; </span><span class="nc">array</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="nf">get</span><span class="p" data-group-id="5435234980-3">(</span><span class="nc">array</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="nf">size</span><span class="p" data-group-id="5435234980-4">(</span><span class="n">A</span><span class="p" data-group-id="5435234980-4">)</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nc">array</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="nf">append</span><span class="p" data-group-id="5435234980-5">(</span><span class="ss">last</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">A</span><span class="p" data-group-id="5435234980-5">)</span><span class="p" data-group-id="5435234980-3">)</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="w">
</span><span class="ss">last</span></code></pre><p>See also <a href="#prepend/2"><code class="inline">prepend/2</code></a>, <a href="#concat/2"><code class="inline">concat/2</code></a>.</p>
  </section>
</section>
<section class="detail" id="concat/1">


