            <h1 class="signature" translate="no">concat(Arrays :: [<a href="#t:array/1">array</a>(Type)])<span class="signature-arrow">&nbsp;-&gt;&nbsp;</span><span class="signature-result"><a href="#t:array/1">array</a>(Type)</span></h1>



          <span class="note">(since OTP @OTP-20004@)</span>


          <a href="https://github.com/erlang/otp/blob/master/lib/stdlib/src/array.erl#L1042" class="icon-action" rel="help nofollow" aria-label="View Source">
