          </a>

      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <section class="docstring">



<p>Concatenates a nonempty list of arrays.</p><h2 id="concat/1-examples" class="section-heading"><a href="#concat/1-examples" class="hover-link"><i class="ri-link-m" aria-hidden="true"></i></a><span class="text">Examples</span></h2><pre><code class="makeup erlang" translate="no"><span class="gp unselectable">1&gt; </span><span class="n">A</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nc">array</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="nf">from_list</span><span class="p" data-group-id="4840975797-1">(</span><span class="p" data-group-id="4840975797-2">[</span><span class="ss">a</span><span class="p" data-group-id="4840975797-2">]</span><span class="p" data-group-id="4840975797-1">)</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="w">
</span><span class="gp unselectable">2&gt; </span><span class="n">B</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nc">array</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="nf">from_list</span><span class="p" data-group-id="4840975797-3">(</span><span class="p" data-group-id="4840975797-4">[</span><span class="ss">b</span><span class="p" data-group-id="4840975797-4">]</span><span class="p" data-group-id="4840975797-3">)</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="w">
</span><span class="gp unselectable">3&gt; </span><span class="nc">array</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="nf">to_list</span><span class="p" data-group-id="4840975797-5">(</span><span class="nc">array</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="nf">concat</span><span class="p" data-group-id="4840975797-6">(</span><span class="p" data-group-id="4840975797-7">[</span><span class="n">A</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">B</span><span class="p" data-group-id="4840975797-7">]</span><span class="p" data-group-id="4840975797-6">)</span><span class="p" data-group-id="4840975797-5">)</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="w">
</span><span class="p" data-group-id="4840975797-8">[</span><span class="ss">a</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="ss">b</span><span class="p" data-group-id="4840975797-8">]</span></code></pre><p>See also <a href="#concat/2"><code class="inline">concat/2</code></a>.</p>
  </section>
</section>
