            <pre translate="no">A = B = AB = <a href="#t:array/1">array</a>(Type)</pre>

        </div>


<p>Concatenates two arrays.</p><p>Adds the elements of <code class="inline">B</code> onto <code class="inline">A</code>.</p><h2 id="concat/2-examples" class="section-heading"><a href="#concat/2-examples" class="hover-link"><i class="ri-link-m" aria-hidden="true"></i></a><span class="text">Examples</span></h2><pre><code class="makeup erlang" translate="no"><span class="gp unselectable">1&gt; </span><span class="n">A</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nc">array</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="nf">set</span><span class="p" data-group-id="5276098677-1">(</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="ss">a</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nc">array</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="nf">new</span><span class="p" data-group-id="5276098677-2">(</span><span class="p" data-group-id="5276098677-3">[</span><span class="p" data-group-id="5276098677-4">{</span><span class="ss">default</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="ss">xa</span><span class="p" data-group-id="5276098677-4">}</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p" data-group-id="5276098677-5">{</span><span class="nb">size</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="mi">3</span><span class="p" data-group-id="5276098677-5">}</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p" data-group-id="5276098677-6">{</span><span class="ss">fixed</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="ss">true</span><span class="p" data-group-id="5276098677-6">}</span><span class="p" data-group-id="5276098677-3">]</span><span class="p" data-group-id="5276098677-2">)</span><span class="p" data-group-id="5276098677-1">)</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="w">
</span><span class="gp unselectable">2&gt; </span><span class="n">B</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nc">array</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="nf">set</span><span class="p" data-group-id="5276098677-7">(</span><span class="mi">2</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="ss">b</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nc">array</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="nf">new</span><span class="p" data-group-id="5276098677-8">(</span><span class="p" data-group-id="5276098677-9">[</span><span class="p" data-group-id="5276098677-10">{</span><span class="ss">default</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="ss">xb</span><span class="p" data-group-id="5276098677-10">}</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p" data-group-id="5276098677-11">{</span><span class="nb">size</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="mi">4</span><span class="p" data-group-id="5276098677-11">}</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p" data-group-id="5276098677-12">{</span><span class="ss">fixed</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="ss">false</span><span class="p" data-group-id="5276098677-12">}</span><span class="p" data-group-id="5276098677-9">]</span><span class="p" data-group-id="5276098677-8">)</span><span class="p" data-group-id="5276098677-7">)</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="w">
</span><span class="gp unselectable">3&gt; </span><span class="n">AB</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nc">array</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="nf">concat</span><span class="p" data-group-id="5276098677-13">(</span><span class="n">A</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">B</span><span class="p" data-group-id="5276098677-13">)</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="w">
</span><span class="gp unselectable">4&gt; </span><span class="nc">array</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="nf">to_list</span><span class="p" data-group-id="5276098677-14">(</span><span class="n">AB</span><span class="p" data-group-id="5276098677-14">)</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="w">
</span><span class="p" data-group-id="5276098677-15">[</span><span class="ss">xa</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="ss">a</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="ss">xa</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="ss">xb</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="ss">xb</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="ss">b</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="ss">xb</span><span class="p" data-group-id="5276098677-15">]</span></code></pre><p>See also <a href="#concat/1"><code class="inline">concat/1</code></a>, <a href="#append/2"><code class="inline">append/2</code></a>, <a href="#prepend/2"><code class="inline">prepend/2</code></a>.</p>
  </section>
</section>
