<p>Gets the value used for uninitialized entries.</p><h2 id="default/1-examples" class="section-heading"><a href="#default/1-examples" class="hover-link"><i class="ri-link-m" aria-hidden="true"></i></a><span class="text">Examples</span></h2><pre><code class="makeup erlang" translate="no"><span class="gp unselectable">1&gt; </span><span class="nc">array</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="nf">default</span><span class="p" data-group-id="1993908014-1">(</span><span class="nc">array</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="nf">new</span><span class="p" data-group-id="1993908014-2">(</span><span class="p" data-group-id="1993908014-2">)</span><span class="p" data-group-id="1993908014-1">)</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="w">
</span><span class="ss">undefined</span><span class="w">
</span><span class="gp unselectable">2&gt; </span><span class="nc">array</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="nf">get</span><span class="p" data-group-id="1993908014-3">(</span><span class="mi">52</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nc">array</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="nf">new</span><span class="p" data-group-id="1993908014-4">(</span><span class="p" data-group-id="1993908014-4">)</span><span class="p" data-group-id="1993908014-3">)</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="w">
</span><span class="ss">undefined</span><span class="w">
</span><span class="gp unselectable">3&gt; </span><span class="nc">array</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="nf">default</span><span class="p" data-group-id="1993908014-5">(</span><span class="nc">array</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="nf">new</span><span class="p" data-group-id="1993908014-6">(</span><span class="p" data-group-id="1993908014-7">[</span><span class="p" data-group-id="1993908014-8">{</span><span class="ss">default</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p" data-group-id="1993908014-8">}</span><span class="p" data-group-id="1993908014-7">]</span><span class="p" data-group-id="1993908014-6">)</span><span class="p" data-group-id="1993908014-5">)</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="w">
</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="w">
</span><span class="gp unselectable">4&gt; </span><span class="nc">array</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="nf">get</span><span class="p" data-group-id="1993908014-9">(</span><span class="mi">52</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nc">array</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="nf">new</span><span class="p" data-group-id="1993908014-10">(</span><span class="p" data-group-id="1993908014-11">[</span><span class="p" data-group-id="1993908014-12">{</span><span class="ss">default</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p" data-group-id="1993908014-12">}</span><span class="p" data-group-id="1993908014-11">]</span><span class="p" data-group-id="1993908014-10">)</span><span class="p" data-group-id="1993908014-9">)</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="w">
</span><span class="mi">0</span></code></pre><p>See also <a href="#new/2"><code class="inline">new/2</code></a>.</p>
