</span><span class="gp unselectable">3&gt; </span><span class="nc">array</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="nf">sparse_to_list</span><span class="p" data-group-id="5305899635-5">(</span><span class="n">A</span><span class="p" data-group-id="5305899635-5">)</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="w">
</span><span class="p" data-group-id="5305899635-6">[</span><span class="ss">x</span><span class="p" data-group-id="5305899635-6">]</span></code></pre><p>See also <a href="#to_list/1"><code class="inline">to_list/1</code></a>  and <a href="#to_orddict/1"><code class="inline">to_orddict/1</code></a>.</p>
