        </div>


<p>Converts the array to an ordered list of pairs <code class="inline">{Index, Value}</code>, skipping
default-valued entries.</p><h2 id="sparse_to_orddict/1-examples" class="section-heading"><a href="#sparse_to_orddict/1-examples" class="hover-link"><i class="ri-link-m" aria-hidden="true"></i></a><span class="text">Examples</span></h2><pre><code class="makeup erlang" translate="no"><span class="gp unselectable">1&gt; </span><span class="n">A</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nc">array</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="nf">from_list</span><span class="p" data-group-id="0993212111-1">(</span><span class="nc">lists</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="nf">seq</span><span class="p" data-group-id="0993212111-2">(</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="mi">2</span><span class="p" data-group-id="0993212111-2">)</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="ss">default</span><span class="p" data-group-id="0993212111-1">)</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="w">
</span><span class="gp unselectable">2&gt; </span><span class="nc">array</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="nf">to_orddict</span><span class="p" data-group-id="0993212111-3">(</span><span class="nc">array</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="nf">reset</span><span class="p" data-group-id="0993212111-4">(</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">A</span><span class="p" data-group-id="0993212111-4">)</span><span class="p" data-group-id="0993212111-3">)</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="w">
</span><span class="p" data-group-id="0993212111-5">[</span><span class="p" data-group-id="0993212111-6">{</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p" data-group-id="0993212111-6">}</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="p" data-group-id="0993212111-7">{</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="ss">default</span><span class="p" data-group-id="0993212111-7">}</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="p" data-group-id="0993212111-8">{</span><span class="mi">2</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="mi">2</span><span class="p" data-group-id="0993212111-8">}</span><span class="p" data-group-id="0993212111-5">]</span><span class="w">
</span><span class="gp unselectable">3&gt; </span><span class="nc">array</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="nf">sparse_to_orddict</span><span class="p" data-group-id="0993212111-9">(</span><span class="nc">array</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="nf">reset</span><span class="p" data-group-id="0993212111-10">(</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">A</span><span class="p" data-group-id="0993212111-10">)</span><span class="p" data-group-id="0993212111-9">)</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="w">
</span><span class="p" data-group-id="0993212111-11">[</span><span class="p" data-group-id="0993212111-12">{</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p" data-group-id="0993212111-12">}</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="p" data-group-id="0993212111-13">{</span><span class="mi">2</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="mi">2</span><span class="p" data-group-id="0993212111-13">}</span><span class="p" data-group-id="0993212111-11">]</span></code></pre><p>See also <a href="#to_orddict/1"><code class="inline">to_orddict/1</code></a>.</p>
