<p>Converts the array to a list.</p><h2 id="to_list/1-examples" class="section-heading"><a href="#to_list/1-examples" class="hover-link"><i class="ri-link-m" aria-hidden="true"></i></a><span class="text">Examples</span></h2><pre><code class="makeup erlang" translate="no"><span class="gp unselectable">1&gt; </span><span class="n">A</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nc">array</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="nf">set</span><span class="p" data-group-id="2143096536-1">(</span><span class="mi">2</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="ss">x</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nc">array</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="nf">new</span><span class="p" data-group-id="2143096536-2">(</span><span class="p" data-group-id="2143096536-2">)</span><span class="p" data-group-id="2143096536-1">)</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="w">
</span><span class="gp unselectable">2&gt; </span><span class="nc">array</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="nf">to_list</span><span class="p" data-group-id="2143096536-3">(</span><span class="n">A</span><span class="p" data-group-id="2143096536-3">)</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="w">
</span><span class="p" data-group-id="2143096536-4">[</span><span class="ss">undefined</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="ss">undefined</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="ss">x</span><span class="p" data-group-id="2143096536-4">]</span></code></pre><p>See also <a href="#from_list/2"><code class="inline">from_list/2</code></a>, <a href="#sparse_to_list/1"><code class="inline">sparse_to_list/1</code></a> and <a href="#to_orddict/1"><code class="inline">to_orddict/1</code></a>.</p>
  </section>
</section>
